the controller takes parameters to control the music daemon :
miamd-controller "$arg"
args:
  f    -> toggle favorite
  s    -> toggle shit
  p    -> toggle pause
  >    -> next
You need a database(either a mysql server or a sqlite file) with a "musics" table containing these rows (sorry for french):

nom                                    | lien                                    | favorite | shit

nom = name
lien = path (can be a youtube link if you have youtube-dl in your $PATH)
miam.conf should be copied to your ~/.config/
